text: Many people may try to show off their superpowers  but no one might be interested in watching them.
Villains will be terrified, they may never come out of hiding.
Cops as well as thieves, both of them may start using their superpowers.
People might start using their superpowers while playing basketball, fans will be disappointed.
Some people might start using their superpowers for just about everything, these people might gain weight.
Many current Superheroes may have to retire.
